WEBVTT

00:00.706 --> 00:01.872
<i>Ty:</i>
<i>Previously on "Heartland":</i>

00:01.873 --> 00:04.475
I think I'll go see
what Amy's doing.

00:04.476 --> 00:06.843
Wouldn't have left her in the lurch
to come water a bunch of cows.

00:06.844 --> 00:07.878
I'm warning you, man.

00:07.879 --> 00:09.513
More than likely...

00:09.514 --> 00:11.449
She'd be begging me
to stay.

00:11.450 --> 00:12.483
(Gate squeaks,
Caleb grunts)

00:12.484 --> 00:13.551
There's problems.

00:13.552 --> 00:16.487
A million problems like...
You're too short.

00:16.488 --> 00:17.454
I'll grow.

00:17.455 --> 00:19.122
Hudson rodeo queen?!

00:19.123 --> 00:21.525
I mean, the next thing you know
you'll be barrel racing.

00:22.526 --> 00:23.793
<i>Kit:</i> <i>Heck, I've been
competing</i> <i>for two years</i>

00:23.794 --> 00:25.161
and you're gonna be
a real threat.

00:25.162 --> 00:26.496
You bet I am.

00:26.497 --> 00:28.731
It's just what I do
with someone I love.

00:28.732 --> 00:29.799
Someone you...

00:29.800 --> 00:32.203
Well, you're never gonna say it,
but that's how I feel.

00:33.204 --> 00:36.072
Maybe we should take a break.

