<i>Boy:</i>
<i>Help!</i>

01:08.737 --> 01:09.670
Help!

01:13.474 --> 01:14.474
Help!

01:14.475 --> 01:15.542
(Horse whinnies)

01:15.543 --> 01:18.112
<i>Man:</i>
<i>Come on! Hyah! Hyah!</i>

01:19.180 --> 01:20.114
Help!

01:22.016 --> 01:23.116
(Water rushes)

01:26.854 --> 01:28.420
<i>Boy:</i>
<i>Help!</i>

01:28.421 --> 01:29.522
(Horse grunts)

01:32.059 --> 01:33.592
(Horse nickers)

01:33.593 --> 01:34.527
Help!

01:40.499 --> 01:41.767
(Water splashes)

01:44.403 --> 01:46.237
Man:
Hang on!

01:46.238 --> 01:47.773
Hold on!

01:47.774 --> 01:49.741
(Breathing heavily)

01:51.310 --> 01:53.344
<i>Hang on, I'm coming!</i>

01:55.380 --> 01:56.513
<i>Boy:</i>
<i>Help!</i>

02:01.920 --> 02:02.887
I'm coming!

02:04.056 --> 02:05.156
(Horse grunts)

02:16.466 --> 02:17.400
Easy...

02:21.939 --> 02:23.606
Man:
Hang on. Hang on.

02:23.607 --> 02:25.108
Hang on.

02:25.109 --> 02:26.041
Boy:
(Coughs)

02:29.112 --> 02:30.478
I'll go get help!

02:31.748 --> 02:32.681
Okay!

02:35.418 --> 02:36.618
You okay?

02:36.619 --> 02:37.586
(Coughs)

02:44.927 --> 02:46.027
(Water rushes)

02:53.568 --> 02:55.168
♪

03:01.342 --> 03:02.942
♪

03:09.016 --> 03:11.451
♪ And at the break of day ♪

03:11.452 --> 03:14.319
♪ you sank into... ♪

03:14.320 --> 03:16.122
♪ your dream ♪

03:16.123 --> 03:17.522
♪ you dreamer ♪

03:17.523 --> 03:20.226
♪ oh, oh, oh... ♪

03:20.227 --> 03:21.560
♪ you dreamer ♪

03:24.297 --> 03:28.634
♪ you dreamer ♪

